## ğŸ“ Project Structure

```
/src
  /controllers     // Route logic
  /models          // SQL models using Sequelize / Knex / Prisma
  /routes          // Express routes
  /middleware      // Auth and error handling
  /config          // DB and environment configs
  /utils           // Helper functions
```

